ComicInfo.Summary: Royal Flush, Queen High: Part Two The Ace Is Played: America's favorite superhero, Ace Justice, intends to clean up New Port City! But after a decade of successful rule under Bomb Queen, will the people want a hero now? Bomb Queen can't help but wonder about the possible connection between Justice's appearance and the upcoming mayoral election. And, if she discovers a plot, she'll take extreme measures to regain control of her city again -- no matter how many she kills in the process!
